      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting with my absolute favorite ride, and let me tell you, it\u2019s been a joy. It\u2019s been my reliable companion for weekend cruises and has that perfect engine purr that only comes from a car that's been truly cared for. It\u2019s got a couple of tiny beauty marks from its adventures on the road, but that just adds character, right? It still looks fantastic parked in the driveway and drives even better. I've handled it with love, and I'm looking for someone who will do the same. Come by, grab a coffee, and let\u2019s get you in the driver\u2019s seat!",
